items.title:
Here’s the 3-step roadmap I wish I had when I started:

1. Subscribe to quality AI newsletters:
The Recap AI (@Lucas Walter | AI Automation)
The Rundown AI (@The Rundown AI)
The Neuron

2. Use ChatGPT daily — apply it to real work, improve your prompts, and even talk to it during your commute.

3. Learn AI automation — start small, like connecting Telegram to ChatGPT with n8n. Learn from 
@Sabrina Ramonov 🍄 
@Stephen | AI Automation
@Chase | AI Guides
@Nate Herkelman

Save this so you can start with just ONE step this week.#aiforbeginners #learnai #aiautomation

